OL,6,FA man has been sentenced to life in
OL,7,Fprison for murdering his friend in
OL,8,FCinderford last year.
OL,10,FMichael Beach had denied the murder of
OL,11,FScott Hopkins and instead had pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to manslaughter, claiming he
OL,13,Fstabbed him in the chest "by accident".
OL,15,FFollowing a week-long trial at
OL,16,FGloucester Crown Court, jurors
OL,17,Freturned a unanimous verdict of guilty
OL,18,Fto the murder and sentenced Beach, 46,
OL,19,Fto a minimum of 17 years behind bars.
