OL,6,FGloucestershire Police were called to
OL,7,Fa property on High Street in
OL,8,FCinderford at 10:20pm on Friday 8
OL,9,FDecember 2023 with a report that a man
OL,10,Fhad been stabbed.
OL,12,FOfficers attended along with
OL,13,Fparamedics, but Scott died at the
OL,14,Fscene from his injuries.
OL,16,FDuring the trial, the court heard how
OL,17,FScott had been drinking with Beach and
OL,18,Fanother friend at a pub in Cinderford
OL,19,Fon the afternoon of the incident, and
OL,20,Fwere said to be in high spirits.
