OL,6,FThe trio returned to a flat on
OL,7,FCinderford High Street that evening to
OL,8,Fcontinue drinking and Scott followed
OL,9,FBeach into the kitchen.
OL,11,FBeach, of Ruspidge Road in Cinderford,
OL,12,Fclaimed he had picked up a kitchen
OL,13,Fknife to chop up some cannabis when
OL,14,FScott came up behind him. He told the
OL,15,Fcourt when giving evidence that he did
OL,16,Fnot know Scott was there and turned
OL,17,Faround and accidentally stabbed him in
OL,18,Fthe chest.
