OL,6,FHe said he thought Scott had wanted to
OL,7,Fgive him a hug, but he pushed him out
OL,8,Fof the way to get past him.
OL,10,FThe jury did not accept Beach's
OL,11,Fversion of events and on Friday (7
OL,12,FJune) they found him guilty of murder.
OL,14,FThe judge said that significant force
OL,15,Fmust have been used in the deliberate
OL,16,Fstabbing.
