OL,6,FThe single knife wound extended 9cm
OL,7,Finto Scott's body, piercing the lung
OL,8,Fand aorta. Despite the best efforts of
OL,9,Femergency services he died at the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,FBodyworn video footage was shown to
OL,13,Fjurors which captured Beach admitting
OL,14,Fto both a police officer and a
OL,15,Fparamedic that he had stabbed Scott.
OL,17,FBeach must serve a minimum term of 17
OL,18,Fyears imprisonment before he is
OL,19,Fconsidered for parole, minus time
OL,20,Falready spent on remand.
