OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, Scott's
OL,7,Ffamily released a statement, which
OL,8,Fsaid: "As a family we would like
OL,9,Feveryone to know Scott had a heart as
OL,10,Fbig as him. At 6ft 1ins his character
OL,11,Fwas as big and bold as he was.
OL,13,F"He will be eternally missed, forever
OL,14,Floved and consistently remembered.
OL,15,FNothing will ever bring Scott back,
OL,16,Fbut this result goes some small way to
OL,17,Fbringing peace to us all.
OL,19,F"We also want to say a huge thank you
OL,20,Fto everyone from the investigation who
OL,21,Fhave helped us since the start.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
