OL,6,F"Every single person has worked so
OL,7,Fhard to support us and get us to this
OL,8,Fpoint. As a family this is the last
OL,9,Fthing we want to say, as the families
OL,10,Fon both sides of this case have young
OL,11,Fchildren who have to now move on with
OL,12,Flives that have changed forever."
OL,14,FSentencing Beach, His Honour Judge
OL,15,FLambert said: "The highly distressing
OL,16,Fnature of this case is accentuated by
OL,17,Fthe fact that we simply do not know
OL,18,Fwhy you did what you did. It may be
OL,19,Fyou do not know either. What we do
OL,20,Fknow is there was absolutely no need
OL,21,Ffor it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
