OL,3,CPolice bodycam captures moment man
OL,4,Cadmits to stabbing his friend
OL,6,F"I detected a good deal of spineless
OL,7,Favoidance by you, both before the
OL,8,Ftrial, and at trial. The jury was sure
OL,9,Fthat your account of pushing the
OL,10,Fdeceased, with a knife in your hand,
OL,11,Fto get past him, when he was about to
OL,12,Fgive you a hug, was another piece of
OL,13,Favoidance.
OL,15,F"Scott was a family man and enjoyed a
OL,16,Fhappy family life with his wife and
OL,17,Ftheir blended family of five. You bear
OL,18,Fthe heaviest burden of responsibility
OL,19,Ffor stealing a loving husband and
OL,20,Ffather from his family."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
