OL,6,FDetective Inspector Adam Stacey, from
OL,7,Fthe Major Crime Investigation Team,
OL,8,Fadded: "Scott was a beloved husband,
OL,9,Fson, brother, father and friend and
OL,10,Fhis death has had an unbearable impact
OL,11,Fon both his loved ones and the tight-
OL,12,Fknit community of Cinderford.
OL,14,F"Beach's senseless actions on that
OL,15,Fnight have torn apart so many lives.
OL,16,FOur thoughts remain with Scott's
OL,17,Ffamily and friends at this incredibly
OL,18,Fdifficult time."
